[I] Python wrapper of libspatialindex for spatial indexing

[T] Python ctypes wrapper of libspatialindex providing spatial indexing
[T] features such as: nearest neighbour, intersection search, multi-dimensional
[T] indexes, clustered indexes, bulk loading, deletion, disk serialization and
[T] custom storage (e.g. ZODB).

[U] https://github.com/Toblerity/rtree

[A] Rtree authors
[M] Paul Manners <paul.manners@yahoo.com>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[E] add libspatialindex

